Phone Number Validation::::


n = input()  # Read input as a string

if len(n) != 10:
    print("Invalid")
else:
    print("Valid")



Kg(s) to Pound(s):::

n = int(input())
p = n * 2.2
print("{:.2f}".format(p))


Reverse of a Numbers:::


n=input()[::-1]
print(n)


To Lower Case::

n=input()
l=n.lower()
print(l)


Area of a Circle:::

PI = 3.14
r = float(input())
area = PI * r * r
print("%.2f" %area)

